title: The Biggest Solution in the Universe - EP. 13
description: Well, since those cocksuckers at http://thebiggestproblemintheuniverse.com/ thought they could screw over their loyal customers with not offering a season pass at a reduced rate I thought it was time for a little rebellion. So I'm hitting them where it hurts, in their pocket. I can't promise future episodes, but this will do for now. Let's let them know that the consumer has a choice. Either give us what we want or we'll take it for free. I introduce to you The Biggest Solution in the Universe episode 13. Comment and share with your friends!!
